name: Signed by whom
text: §445-3  Signed by whom.  Every license shall be signed by the treasurer of the county, within which the license is to be operative. [L 1890, c 28, §3; am L 1909, c 151, §3; am L 1913, c 99, §1; am L 1915, c 89, §1; RL 1925, §1957; RL 1935, §2402; RL 1945, §7003; RL 1955, §155-3; am L 1967, c 248, §1; HRS §445-3; gen ch 1985; am L 1990, c 164, §4]
